Class ScenesController

java.lang.Object
javafx.application.Application
pl.polsl.lab.ScenesController
public class ScenesController
extends javafx.application.Application
Class used to contain JavaFXs stage and scenes. This class contains application scenes in a Map data structure. Class extends Application class.
